"title": "5297: disease",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5297",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An illness or other condition which prevents people or animals from achieving their full potential or adversely affects their abilities.</p>\n<h2>General and specific examples of disease</h2>\n<h3>General references</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:17\">MAT 8:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:10\">MRK 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:26\">EXO 15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:15\">DEU 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:12\">2CH 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:3\">JHN 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:9\">ACT 28:9</a></p>\n<h3>Blindness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:1\">JHN 9:1</a></p>\n<h3>Boils and sores</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:9\">EXO 9:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:7\">JOB 2:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:21\">ISA 38:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:20\">LUK 16:20</a></p>\n<h3>Depression</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:12\">PRO 13:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Dropsy</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:2\">LUK 14:2</a></p>\n<h3>Dysentery</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:8\">ACT 28:8</a></p>\n<h3>Epilepsy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:15\">MAT 17:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:24\">MAT 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:17-Mark9:18\">MRK 9:17–9:18</a></p>\n<h3>Fever</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:30\">JOB 30:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:14\">MAT 8:14</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:30\">MRK 1:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:38\">LUK 4:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:8\">ACT 28:8</a></p>\n<h3>Haemorrhaging</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:20\">MAT 9:20</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:25\">MRK 5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:43\">LUK 8:43</a></p>\n<h3>Inflammation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:22\">DEU 28:22</a></p>\n<h3>Insanity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam21:13\">1SA 21:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:33-Dan4:35\">DAN 4:33–4:35</a></p>\n<h3>Leprosy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:10\">NUM 12:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:21\">2CH 26:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:5\">MAT 11:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:11-Luke17:19\">LUK 17:11–17:19</a></p>\n<h3>Paralysis</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:24\">MAT 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:6\">MAT 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2\">MAT 9:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:3\">MRK 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:18\">LUK 5:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:11\">LUK 13:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:2\">ACT 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:7\">ACT 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:33\">ACT 9:33</a></p>\n<h3>Sunstroke</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:18-2Kgs4:19\">2KI 4:18–4:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:5-Ps121:6\">PSA 121:5–121:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:10\">ISA 49:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:8\">JON 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Tumours</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:27\">DEU 28:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:6\">1SA 5:6</a></p>\n<h3>Voluntary starvation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:7\">1SA 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:20\">1SA 28:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:4\">PSA 102:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:18\">PSA 107:18</a></p>\n<h3>Wasting</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:16\">LEV 26:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:22\">DEU 28:22</a></p>\n<h2>Even the righteous suffer disease</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:3\">JOB 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:7\">JOB 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:2-Ps38:3\">PSA 38:2–38:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:7-Ps41:8\">PSA 41:7–41:8</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of the righteous suffering</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:1\">2KI 20:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:24\">2CH 32:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:27\">DAN 8:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:2\">LUK 7:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:1\">JHN 11:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:36-Acts9:37\">ACT 9:36–9:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:13\">GAL 4:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:25-Phil2:27\">PHP 2:25–2:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:23\">1TI 5:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:20\">2TI 4:20</a></p>\n<h2>Causes of disease</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:2\">JHN 9:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Original sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16-Gen3:17\">GEN 3:16–3:17</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Accident</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:39-2Kgs4:40\">2KI 4:39–4:40</a></p>\n<h3>Judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:17-Ps107:18\">PSA 107:17–107:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:8-Exod9:10\">EXO 9:8–9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:14-Lev26:16\">LEV 26:14–26:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:41-Num16:49\">NUM 16:41–16:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:27\">2KI 5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:12\">JER 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:29-1Cor11:30\">1CO 11:29–11:30</a></p>\n<h3>Testing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:5\">JOB 2:5</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Response to sickness and disease</h2>\n<h3>The compassion of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:32-Mark1:34\">MRK 1:32–1:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:3\">PSA 41:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:17\">MAT 8:17</a></p>\n<h3>Compassion</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:4\">EZK 34:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:36\">MAT 25:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:2\">LUK 9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:30-Luke10:37\">LUK 10:30–10:37</a></p>\n<h3>Humble submission</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:15\">JOB 13:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:8-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:8–12:10</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:14\">JAS 5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:17\">GEN 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:8\">2CO 12:8</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual disease</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:5-Isa1:6\">ISA 1:5–1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:22\">JER 8:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:12\">JER 30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:9\">MIC 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:12-Matt9:13\">MAT 9:12–9:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:31-Luke5:32\">LUK 5:31–5:32</a></p>\n<h2>Salvation and healing from disease</h2>\n<h3>Salvation achieved through the cross of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:4-Isa53:5\">ISA 53:4–53:5</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Salvation made perfect in heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1-Rev22:3\">REV 22:1–22:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:12\">EZK 47:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:17\">REV 7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:4\">REV 21:1–21:4</a></p>",
